details.name: HIT - Get On My Level
details.creator: -Hitokiri-
details.desc: Every single bike works. Non-contact mode is preferred, but not necessary. Get ready for the jumps, tubes, wall rides, trenches, sharp turns, tight ropes, obstacle lines, & water crossing. But If you manage to go through all this hell before ur opponents then you'll have a privilege to say to them, ''Get on my level'' and this time it will make literal sense... Features the 1st bike elevator in GTA. GTA mode is available.
